{"tid":2337802,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"路透社：意大利電訊擬減少購買華為 5G 網絡設備","createTime":"2020-12-23T14:23:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-23T16:49:32.000Z","uid":48083,"like":6,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"4ea735fb6d0ca8920ed568735343d4dbbf64e8ce","tid":2337802,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T14:23:01.000Z","msg":"路透社今日（ 23 日）引消息報道，意大利電訊（ Telecom Italia ）決定保留 Nokia 為 5G 網絡設備供應商，以減少華為供應建設 5G 網絡設備的比率。重新檢視的合約中，瑞典的愛立信（ Sweden's Ericsson ）將供應大部分設備，華為及 Nokia 則會得到 20 至 25 %的合約；有關減少合約比率的談判仍在進行中。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/international/%E8%B7%AF%E9%80%8F%E7%A4%BE-%E6%84%8F%E5%A4%A7%E5%88%A9%E9%9B%BB%E8%A8%8A%E6%93%AC%E6%B8%9B%E5%B0%91%E8%B3%BC%E8%B2%B7%E8%8F%AF%E7%82%BA-5g-%E7%B6%B2%E7%B5%A1%E8%A8%AD%E5%82%99/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E8%25B7%25AF%25E9%2580%258F%25E7%25A4%25BE-%25E6%2584%258F%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%2588%25A9%25E9%259B%25BB%25E8%25A8%258A%25E6%2593%25AC%25E6%25B8%259B%25E5%25B0%2591%25E8%25B3%25BC%25E8%25B2%25B7%25E8%258F%25AF%25E7%2582%25BA-5g-%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E7%25B5%25A1%25E8%25A8%25AD%25E5%2582%2599%2F&d=djscsuFvXcghIMf2lgFVp%2F3ZlJXgeXtiTXALECG4O5Q%3D&h=e967dd04\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E8%25B7%25AF%25E9%2580%258F%25E7%25A4%25BE-%25E6%2584%258F%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%2588%25A9%25E9%259B%25BB%25E8%25A8%258A%25E6%2593%25AC%25E6%25B8%259B%25E5%25B0%2591%25E8%25B3%25BC%25E8%25B2%25B7%25E8%258F%25AF%25E7%2582%25BA-5g-%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E7%25B5%25A1%25E8%25A8%25AD%25E5%2582%2599%2F&h=56c45d48\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/international/%E8%B7%AF%E9%80%8F%E7%A4%BE-%E6%84%8F%E5%A4%A7%E5%88%A9%E9%9B%BB%E8%A8%8A%E6%93%AC%E6%B8%9B%E5%B0%91%E8%B3%BC%E8%B2%B7%E8%8F%AF%E7%82%BA-5g-%E7%B6%B2%E7%B5%A1%E8%A8%AD%E5%82%99/</a>"},{"pid":"3b9c1429c6bc82a3778857394c39ac6e2e03d72c","tid":2337802,"uid":261505,"like":2,"dislike":1,"